        <div xml:id="TK75">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>aṉpuṟ ṟamarnta vaḻakkeṉpa vaiyakat</l>
<l>tiṉpuṟṟā reytuñ ciṟappu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>They say that the felicity which those who, after enjoying the pleasure (of the conjugal state) in this world, obtain in heaven is the result of their domestic state imbued with love.</l>
            </lg>
